  "title": "Technician, Science MNC (1-Year Contract) - WEST #HHL",
  "description": "<p>Location: Gul <br />Salary: 2000<br />Working hour: 5 days office hour</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Assemble single-use bio-processing containers following technical drawings and work instructions to meet quality standards</li><li>Operate effectively within a Class 7 cleanroom environment to maintain product sterility and safety</li><li>Accurately complete batch records in compliance with Good Documentation Practices (GDP) to ensure traceability and quality control</li><li>Follow ISO and current Good Manufacturing Practice (cGMP) requirements to uphold regulatory and safety standards</li><li>Collaborate with engineers and Quality Assurance teams to support production and quality objectives</li><li>Maintain a clean and safe work environment by adhering to safety protocols and housekeeping standards</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum O Level /NITEC, preferably in Science or Engineering</li><li>Willingness to learn and adapt through provided training</li><li>Interest in working within the medical device industry</li></ul><p>If interested, please email me at alexgoh@recruitexpress.com.sg or telegram @alexgohhl<br /><br />Alex Goh Hock Leong (CEI.No: R1763413 | Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Life Science) | 99C4599)</p>",
